Instalación de certificados mediante apt
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install ca-certificates curl gnupg
$ sudo install -m 0755 -d /etc/apt/keyrings
$ curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o
$ sudo chmod a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg
//Agregar los repositorios a las fuentes APT
$ echo \"deb [arch="$(dpkg --print-architecture)" signed-by=etc/apt/keyrings/docker.gpg] https://download.docekr.com/linux/ubuntu \ "$(. etc/os-release && echo "$VERSION_CODENAME")" stable" | \ 
sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list > /dev/null

Coamando para instalar Docker
$ sudo apt-get install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-buildx-plugin docker-compose-plugin
$ sudo docker ps  -> comando para ejecutar docker

